{"author":"Sunan Ibn Majah","hadith":{"hadithnumber":3528,"arabicnumber":3528,"text":"। আয়েশা (রাঃ) থেকে বর্ণিত। নবী সাল্লাল্লাহু আলাইহি ওয়াসাল্লাম কিছু পড়ে ঝাড়ফুঁক করতেন।","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Fouad Abd al-Baqi","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Sahih"}],"reference":{"book":31,"hadith":93}}}